[{"id":"591b7362c138a86ab33fb03be541ebac","from":"J. Epstein","from_email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to":"Craig@PenumbraMarine.com","to_list":[{"name":"Craig@PenumbraMarine.com","email":"Craig@PenumbraMarine.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Re: Limitless","date":"2007-05-11T22:08:04.000Z","formatted_date":"May 11, 2007","formatted_time":"10:08 PM","body":"no interest,, i still have not heard of the fastest tender \n\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Craig <Craig@penumbramarine.com>\nTo: DKIESQ@aol.com; J. Epstein <jeeproject@yahoo.com>\nSent: Friday, May 11, 2007 12:42:25 PM\nSubject: Limitless\n\n\nDear Darren,\n \nI just received a call from someone that is interested in Purchasing LIMITLESS. I don\u2019t believe he is another $200m buyer as before (that one was rare and he ended up building a 132m yacht), but definitely qualified and wanting to move very soon on something in the 100 meter range. \n \nFYI \u2013 I think we might be able to go north of $150m if M/M Wexner\u2019 are interested.  Can you please drop them an email or call to see if she can be purchased?\n \nRegards,\n \nCraig Tafoya\nPenumbra Marine Logistics\n(954) 328-6203\nhttp://www.CraigTafoya.com","body_html":"<html><head><style type=\"text/css\"><!-- DIV {margin:0px;} --></style></head><body><div style=\"font-family:times new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt\"><DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">no interest,, i still have not heard of the fastest tender <BR><BR>\n<DIV style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif\">----- Original Message ----<BR>From: Craig &lt;Craig@penumbramarine.com&gt;<BR>To: DKIESQ@aol.com; J. Epstein &lt;jeeproject@yahoo.com&gt;<BR>Sent: Friday, May 11, 2007 12:42:25 PM<BR>Subject: Limitless<BR><BR>\n<STYLE>\n<!--\n _filtered {font-family:\"Brush Script MT\";panose-1:3 6 8 2 4 4 6 7 3 4;}\n _filtered {font-family:\"BankGothic Md BT\";panose-1:2 11 8 7 2 2 3 6 2 4;}\n/* Style Definitions */\n p.MsoNormal, li.MsoNormal, div.MsoNormal\n\t{margin:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:\"Times New Roman\";}\na:link, span.MsoHyperlink\n\t{color:blue;text-decoration:underline;}\na:visited, span.MsoHyperlinkFollowed\n\t{color:purple;text-decoration:underline;}\nspan.EmailStyle17\n\t{font-family:\"Times New Roman\";color:navy;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;text-decoration:none none;}\n _filtered {margin:1.0in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\ndiv.Section1\n\t{}\n-->\n</STYLE>\n\n<DIV class=Section1>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=navy size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: navy\">Dear Darren,</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=navy size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: navy\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=navy size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: navy\">I just received a call from someone that is interested in Purchasing LIMITLESS. I don\u2019t believe he is another $200m buyer as before (that one was rare and he ended up building a 132m yacht), but definitely qualified and wanting to move very soon on something in the 100 meter range. </SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=navy size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: navy\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=navy size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: navy\">FYI \u2013 I think we might be able to go north of $150m if M/M Wexner\u2019 are interested.&nbsp; Can you please drop them an email or call to see if she can be purchased?</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=navy size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: navy\">&nbsp;</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\" color=navy size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: navy\">Regards,</SPAN></FONT></P>\n<P class=MsoNormal><FONT face=\"Times 